These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, peas, pineapple, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, indie, r&b, rock
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, time-travel, zombie
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, gardening, skydiving, card-games
House: victorian, art-deco, ranch-style, palace
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, monopoly, poker
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, subway, tram
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the victorian house##1
 3. the person eating pineapple is not the person driving the car##6
 4. the person driving the subway is not the person eating peas##6
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
 6. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
 7. the person driving the tram is not the person playing snooker##6
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of techno##1
 9. the fan of r&b is not the person eating raspberry##6
10. the fan of rock is the person driving the car##1
11. the fan of r&b is the person driving the boat##1
12. the victorian house is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing poker##1
14. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the fan of indie##5
15. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
16. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the tram##7
17. the person playing poker is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
18. the art-deco house is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
19. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person playing chess##7
20. the art-deco house is not the person eating raspberry##6
21. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | cabbage      | raspberry   | peas     | pineapple |
| Music-Genre           | rock | indie   | techno    | r&b     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie       | time-travel | horror   | mystery   |
| Hobby   | skydiving      | card-games     | collecting | gardening    |
| House           | art-deco   | palace       | ranch-style  | victorian       |
| Game         | chess     | snooker     | monopoly | poker   |
| Transport     | car          | subway      | tram     | boat      |

