 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
12. the person traveling to miami is not the person who likes orange##6
13. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
14. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
15. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
16. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
17. the person driving the airplane is the person who's birthday is in september##1
18. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
19. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
20. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
21. the brazilian is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
